generic:link.msg:message: Identity " Value of 'Capital ' ( = (i) Equity Capital + (ii) Perpetual / Non Redeemable Preference Shares + (iii)) Non-Perpetual / Redeemable Preference Shares + (iv) Others )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Reserves & Surplus' ( = (i) Share Premium Account + (ii) General Reserves + (iii) Statutory/Special Reserve (Section 45-IC reserve to be shown separately below item no.(vii)) + (iv) Reserves under Sec 45-IC of RBI Act 1934 + (v) Capital Redemption Reserve + (vi) Debenture Redemption Reserve + (vii) Other Capital Reserves + (viii) Other Revenue Reserves + (ix) Investment Fluctuation Reserves/ Investment Reserves + (x) Revaluation Reserves (a+b) + (xi) Share Application Money Pending Allotment + (xii) Others (Please mention) + (xiii) Balance of profit and loss account) )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Revaluation Reserves' ( = (a) Revl. Reserves - Property + (b) Revl. Reserves - Financial Assets )" do not tally

Identity " Value of ' Bonds & Notes ' ( = (i) Plain Vanilla Bonds (As per residual maturity of the instruments) + (ii) Bonds with embedded call / put options including zero coupon / deep discount bonds ( As per residual period for the earliest exercise date for the embedded option) + (iii) Fixed Rate Notes) )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Deposits (i+ii)' ( = (i) Term Deposits from Public + (ii) Others)" do not tally.

Identity " Value of 'Borrowings' ( = (i) Bank Borrowings (a+b+c+d+e+f) + (ii) Inter Corporate Deposits (Other than Related Parties) (These being institutional / wholesale deposits, shall be slotted as per their residual maturity) + (iii) Loans from Related Parties (including ICDs) + (iv) Corporate Debts + (v) Borrowings from Central Government / State Government + (vi) Borrowings from RBI + (vii) Borrowings from Public Sector Undertakings (PSUs) + (viii) Borrowings from Others (Please specify) + (ix) Commercial Papers (CPs) + (x) Non - Convertible Debentures (NCDs) (A+B) + (xi) Convertible Debentures (A+B) (Debentures with embedded call / put options As per residual period for the earliest exercise date for the embedded option) + (xii) Subordinate Debt + (xiii) Perpetual Debt Instrument + (xiv) Security Finance Transactions(a+b+c+d) )" do not tally

Identity " Value of ' Bank Borrowings ' ( = (a) Bank Borrowings in the nature of Term Money Borrowings + b) Bank Borrowings in the nature of WCDL + c) Bank Borrowings in the nature of Cash Credit (CC) + d) Bank Borrowings in the nature of Letter of Credit (LCs) + e) Bank Borrowings in the nature of ECBs + (f) Other bank borrowings) )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Commercial Papers (CPs)' ( = (a) To Mutual Funds + (b) To Banks + (c) To NBFCs + (d) To Insurance Companies + (e) To Pension Funds + (f) To Others (Please specify) )" do not tally
Identity " Value of ' Non - Convertible Debentures (NCDs)' ( = Secured + Un-Secured )" do not tally

Identity " Value of ' Non-Convertible Debentures - Secured ' ( = (a) Subscribed by Retail Investors + (b) Subscribed by Banks + (c) Subscribed by NBFCs + (d) Subscribed by Mutual Funds + (e) Subscribed by Insurance Companies + (f) Subscribed by Pension Funds + (g) Others (Please specify) )" do not tally

Identity " Value of ' Non-Convertible Debentures - UnSecured ' ( = (a) Subscribed by Retail Investors + (b) Subscribed by Banks + (c) Subscribed by NBFCs + (d) Subscribed by Mutual Funds + (e) Subscribed by Insurance Companies + (f) Subscribed by Pension Funds + (g) Others (Please specify) )" do not tally

Identity "Value of Convertible Debentures (A+B) (Debentures with embedded call / put options As per residual period for the earliest exercise date for the embedded option) = [A. Secured (a+b+c+d+e+f+g) + B. Un-Secured (a+b+c+d+e+f+g)]" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Convertible Debentures - Secured' ( = (a) Subscribed by Retail Investors + (b) Subscribed by Banks + (c) Subscribed by NBFCs + (d) Subscribed by Mutual Funds + (e) Subscribed by Insurance Companies + (f) Subscribed by Pension Funds + (g) Others (Please specify) )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Convertible Debentures - UnSecured ' ( = (a) Subscribed by Retail Investors + (b) Subscribed by Banks + (c) Subscribed by NBFCs + (d) Subscribed by Mutual Funds + (e) Subscribed by Insurance Companies + (f) Subscribed by Pension Funds + (g) Others (Please specify) )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Security Finance Transactions' ( = (a) Repo, b) Reverse Repo, c) CBLO, d) Others )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Current Liabilities & Provision' ( = (a) Sundry creditors + b) Expenses payable (Other than Interest) + (c) Advance income received from borrowers pending adjustment + (d) Interest payable on deposits and borrowings + (e) Provisions for Standard Assets + (f) Provisions for Non Performing Assets (NPAs) + (g) Provisions for Investment Portfolio (NPI) + (h) Other Provisions (Please Specify) )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Unclaimed Deposits ' ( = (i) Pending for less than 7 years + (ii) Pending for greater than 7 years )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Outflows On Account of Off Balance Sheet (OBS) Exposure' ( =(i)Loan commitments pending disbursal + (ii)Lines of credit committed to other institution + (iii)Total Letter of Credits + (iv)Total Guarantees + (v) Bills discounted/rediscounted + (vi)Total Derivative Exposures + (vii)Others )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Total Derivative Exposures' ( = (a) Forward Forex Contracts + (b) Futures Contracts + (c) Options Contracts + (d) Forward Rate Agreements + (e) Swaps - Currency + (f) Swaps - Interest Rate + (g) Credit Default Swaps + (h) Other Derivatives )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'TOTAL OUTFLOWS ' ( = 1.Capital + 2.Reserves & Surplus + 3.Gifts, Grants, Donations & Benefactions + 4.Bonds & Notes + 5.Deposits + 6.Borrowings + 7.Current Liabilities & Provisions + 8.Statutory Dues + 9.Unclaimed Deposits +10.Any Other Unclaimed Amount + 11.Debt Service Realisation Account + 12.Other Outflows + 13.Outflows On Account of Off Balance Sheet (OBS) Exposure)" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Balances With Banks' ( = (a) Current Account + b) Deposit Accounts /Short-Term Deposits) )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Investments (Net of Provisions)' ( = (i)Statutory Investments (only for NBFCs-D) + (ii) Listed Investments + (iii) Unlisted Investments + (iv) Venture Capital Units + (v) Others (Please Specify) )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Listed Investment or Unlisted Investment ' ( = Current + Non-current )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Non-Performing Loans (Net of Provisions)' ( = (i) Bills of Exchange and Promissory Notes discounted & rediscounted + (ii) Term Loans + (iii) Interest to be serviced through regular schedule + (iv) Interest to be serviced to be in Bullet Payment )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Term Loans' ( = (a) Through Regular Payment Schedule + (b) Through Bullet Payment) )" do not tally
Identity " Value of ' Non-Performing Loans (Net of Provisions) ' ( = (i) Substandard + (ii) Doubtful and loss." do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Non-Performing Loans (Net of Provisions) Substandard ' ( = (a) All overdues and instalments of principal falling due during the next three years + (b) Entire principal amount due beyond the next three years )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Non-Performing Loans (Net of Provisions) Doubtful and loss' ( = (a) All instalments of principal falling due during the next five years as also all overdues + (b) Entire principal amount due beyond the next five years )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Other Assets ' ( = (a) Intangible assets & other non-cash flow items + (b) Other items (e.g. accrued income, other receivables, staff loans, etc.) + (c) Others )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Security Finance Transactions' ( = (a) Repo, b) Reverse Repo, c) CBLO, d) Others )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Inflows On Account of Off Balance Sheet (OBS) Exposure' ( = (i) Loan commited by other institution pending disbursal + (ii) Lines of credit committed by other institution + (iii) Bills discounted/rediscounted + (iv)Total Derivative Exposures + (v)Others )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Total Derivative Exposures' ( = (a) Forward Forex Contracts + (b) Futures Contracts + (c) Options Contracts + (d) Forward Rate Agreements + (e) Swaps - Currency + (f) Swaps - Interest Rate + (g) Credit Default Swaps + (h) Other Derivatives )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'TOTAL INFLOWS ' ( = 1. Cash + 2. Remittance in Transit + 3. Balances With Banks + 4.Investments (Net of Provisions) + 5.Advances (Performing) + 6.Non-Performing Loans (Net of Provisions) + 7. Inflows From Assets On Lease + 8. Fixed Assets (Excluding Assets On Lease) + 9. Other Assets + 10.Security Finance Transactions + 11.Inflows On Account of Off Balance Sheet (OBS) Exposure )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Mismatch (B - A) ' ( =TOTAL INFLOWS - TOTAL OUTFLOWS)" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for the period of 0 to 7 Days ( ='Mismatch' for the same period )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for the period of 15 days to 30/31 Days ( = 'Mismatch' for the period of 15 days to 30/31 Days + 'Cumulative mismatch' for the period of 8 to 14 Days )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over one month to 2 months( = 'Mismatch' for Over one month to 2 months + Cumulative mismatch for 15 to 30/31 days )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for the period over one month to 2 months ( = 'Mismatch' for the period over one month and to 3 months + 'Cumulative mismatch' for over one month to 2 months )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over 3 months to 6 months ( = 'Mismatch' for Over 3 months to 6 months + Cumulative mismatch for over 2 months to 3 months )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over 6 months to one year ( = 'Mismatch' for Over 6 months to one year plus Cumulative mismatch for over 3 months to 6 months )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over one year to 3 years ( = 'Mismatch' for Over one year to 3 years + Cumulative mismatch for Over 6 months to one year )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over 3 to 5 years ( = 'Mismatch' for Over 3 to 5 years plus Cumulative mismatch for Over one year to 3 years )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over 5 years ( = 'Mismatch' for Over 5 years + Cumulative mismatch for Over 3 to 5 years )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Total Cumulative mismatch' ( = Cumulative mismatch for Over 5 years )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Mismatch as % of Total Outflows' ( =Mismatch (B - A) / TOTAL OUTFLOWS)" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Total Structural Liquidity' ( = (0 to 7 Days + 8 day to 14 days + 15 days to 30/31 days (One month) + Over one month and upto 2 months + Over two months and upto 3 months + Over 3 months and upto 6 months + Over 6 months and upto 1 year + Over 1 year and upto 3 years + Over 3 years and upto 5 years + Over 5 years )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for 8 day to 14 days ( = 'Mismatch' for 8 day to 14 days + Cumulative mismatch for 0 day to 7 days )" do not tally
Identity " Value of ' C as percentage Of A' ( = Mismatch (B - A) / TOTAL OUTFLOWS (A) for actual outflow or inflow )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative Mismatch as % of Cumulative Total Outflows' ( = 'Cumulative Mismatch' / 'Cumulative Outflows')" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative Mismatch as % of Cumulative Total Outflows' ( = 'Cumulative Mismatch' / 'Cumulative Outflows')" do not tally
"If ""Mismatch (B - A)"" is positive then ""Mismatch as % of Total Outflows"" should be positive. If ""Mismatch (B - A)"" is negative then ""Mismatch as % of Total Outflows"" should be negative."

"If ""Cumulative Mismatch"" is positive then ""Cumulative Mismatch as % of Cumulative Total Outflows"" should be positive. If ""Cumulative Mismatch"" is negative then ""Cumulative Mismatch as % of Cumulative Total Outflows"" should be negative."
